Package: gmov
Title: Generative Movement Validation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Aurélien",
        family = "Nicosia",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "116816597+AurelienNicosiaULaval@users.noreply.github.com"
    )
Description: Implements trajectory-level generative validation diagnostics for
    simulations from fitted step selection function and integrated step
    selection function models. The package is designed as a lightweight
    companion to 'amt': users fit and simulate movement models elsewhere, then
    use this package to compare observed and simulated trajectories with
    trajectory-level summaries.
